longBusinessSummary: Ecolomondo Corporation, a development stage clean tech company, designs, engineers, and develops a thermal decomposition process using a pyrolysis platform that converts hydrocarbon waste into marketable commodity end-products, namely carbon black substitute, oil, gas, and steel. Ecolomondo Corporation is headquartered in Saint-Laurent, Canada.
